// Kodex Topic Detail
// Full view of a single Kodex topic with content sections, draft comparison, alias management,
// flagging, verification, and deletion.

FUNCTION ConfidenceBadge(confidence)
  Render a colored badge for confidence level.

---

FUNCTION ContentSection(title, content)
  Render a titled block of pre-formatted topic content. Hidden if content is empty.

---

FUNCTION MermaidBlock(content)
  CALLS: mermaid.render (mermaid)
  On mount or content change: render the Mermaid diagram into the container div.
  Show an error block if rendering fails.

---

FUNCTION DiagramsSection(content)
  CALLS: MermaidBlock (TopicDetail)
  Parse the content for ```mermaid fenced code blocks.
  Render MermaidBlock for each diagram and plain text for non-diagram sections.

---

FUNCTION DraftComparisonSection(title, liveContent, draftContent)
  Render a side-by-side diff row for one content field. Show a 'Changed' badge if content differs.

---

FUNCTION TopicDetail()                                                  EXPORT
  CALLS: getTopic (kodex-api), listDrafts (kodex-api), createFlag (kodex-api), verifyTopic (kodex-api), deleteTopic (kodex-api), approveDraft (kodex-api), rejectDraft (kodex-api), addAlias (kodex-api), removeAlias (kodex-api)
  Read topic name from URL params. Read selectedProject from kodexStore.
  On mount: fetch the topic via kodexApi.getTopic.
  If topic.hasDraft: auto-load the draft via kodexApi.listDrafts to populate the comparison.

  handleFlag: submit a new flag via kodexApi.createFlag.
  handleVerify: call kodexApi.verifyTopic('user'), then reload the topic.
  handleDelete: require the user to type the topic name to confirm, then call kodexApi.deleteTopic
    and navigate to /kodex/topics.
  handleApproveDraft: call kodexApi.approveDraft, then reload the topic.
  handleRejectDraft: confirm, call kodexApi.rejectDraft, then reload the topic.
  handleAddAlias / handleRemoveAlias: call the respective kodexApi methods, then reload the topic.

  Render:
    - Header with title, slug, confidence badge, verified/draft indicators, and AliasEditor.
    - Action bar: Verify, Flag Topic, Delete Topic buttons.
    - Delete confirmation modal (requires typing topic name).
    - Flag form (type + description input).
    - Draft comparison section (if topic has a draft): side-by-side DraftComparisonSection per field.
    - Content sections (if no draft): ContentSection blocks + DiagramsSection.
